  2. Decision-Making Logic (the brain in detail)

  Everything below happens inside one run_conversation() call. This is the agent's actual decision policy.

  2.1 The outer loop

  run_conversation()  [agent/conversation_loop.py:371-4244]
  │
  ├─ turn_context.build_turn_context()           [prologue: sanitize, prompt, preflight compress, memory prefetch]
  │
  ├─ while api_call_count < max_iterations AND iteration_budget.remaining > 0:    [L461]
  │   │
  │   ├─ inner retry loop  [L811+]               [credentials / image shrink / context / fallback]
  │   │   └─ provider API call
  │   │
  │   ├─ post-response dispatch  [L3300+]
  │   │    ├─ tool_calls present  → execute, append results, continue   [L3502+]
  │   │    ├─ text-only + finish_reason=="stop"  → break                  [L4164]
  │   │    ├─ truncated response → length-continuation retry (3 max)     [L1315-1508]
  │   │    └─ empty response   → thinking prefill or fallback (3 max)    [L3970+]
  │   │
  │   └─ post-turn: should_compress(real_usage)? → compress              [L3815]
  │
  ├─ grace call (1 free API call after budget==0)  [L480-481]
  └─ finalize_turn() [agent/turn_finalizer.py:30]

  2.2 The five "decide what to do next" branches

  Each branch is the agent's actual choice surface — every other piece of the system feeds into one of these:

  ┌──────────────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
  │            Branch            │                          Decided by                          │                                     Trigger                                      │
  ├──────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
  │ Continue with tool execution │ Presence of tool_calls, validated args                       │ conversation_loop.py:3502                                                        │
  ├──────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
